# UserDefaultTypes Object

- `string` string
- `boolean` boolean
- `integer` number
- `float` number
- `double` number
- `url` string
- `array` Array\<unknown\>
- `dictionary` Record\<string, unknown\>

This type is a helper alias, no object will ever exist of this type.
